| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4695 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1c691f2d-9cf4-5df1-a6b1-2edcf442b74a"
index=*
